evious member of the nasd investment company committee about archer archer is a privately owned and operated technology and services innovator for the investment management industry whose clients manage more than  trillion in assets archer offers simplified technology solutions and selective operations outsourcing which give investment managers stable and controllable infrastructure to facilitate growth  disclaimer  news data and statement included in this release are intended exclusively for information purposes product and brand names used in this release maybe trademarks or registered trade marks of their respective owners talentboards accepts neither liability for the consequences of the reader’s reliance nor responsibility for the adequacy or accuracy of this release no data or statement in this release should be considered a recommendation for the purchase retention or sale of the securities referred to hereinother related postsanglo pacific group appointed david archer to the board as independent nonexecutive directorfidessa group appointed ken archer to its board as nonexecutive directorarcher daniels midland appoints suzan harrison to its board of directorstalentboards teamhere the original post  comments are closed latest boardroom news centerstate banks appoints david salyers to the board of directors july   insight engines announces david hornik and erik swan to board along with raising m series a funding led by august capital july   plexchat announces gordon rubenstein to its board along with raising m seed funding led by raine ventures july   square appoints randy garutti to its board of directors july   temperpack announces robert beckler and cody nystrom to board along with raising m series a financing led by sjf ventures july   random boardsnowsecureboingo wirelessreceivables exchangeeasypropertypq bypass    talentboards inc  all rights reserved  geneva  miami  london  boston  paris  shanghai  monaco